title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Boeing 737-700 - Configuring flight plans
description:
In this video we are going to look at the 2 different methods how to program a flight in the FMC from the PMDG Boeing 737-700. We will use simbrief.com for creating the flight plan and show you both the method how to load it easily by using a saved file and putting it in manually.

00:00 intro
00:10 creating the flight plan using Simbrief.com
05:48 loading the saved flight plan into the FMC
10:25 manually adding the flight plan into the FMC

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://pmdg.com/pmdg-737-700-for-microsoft-flight-simulator/
